{"tid":2010171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"確認新冠病毒抗體  德研究機構獲突破性進展","createTime":"2020-05-10T08:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T12:11:06.000Z","uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92f85360e37d95762a989eb911d1a318106cc708","tid":2010171,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.dw.com/image/52922109_303.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fimage%2F52922109_303.jpg&h=a2f3c97d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>利用新冠病毒康復患者的血清治療重症病人，是一種廣泛採用的療法。能否人工製造抗體，協助治療病患呢？現在，德國科研人員在這方面取得了重大突破。</strong><br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://p.dw.com/p/3brky\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.dw.com%2Fp%2F3brky&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=7ceea19e\" target=\"_blank\">https://p.dw.com/p/3brky</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dw.chinese.traditional/posts/879197792582865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdw.chinese.traditional%2Fposts%2F879197792582865&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=1ff7a7c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dw.chinese.traditional/posts/879197792582865</a>"},{"pid":"aedb52d24da1cf39f4af49b73a348b5ecd4e1809","tid":2010171,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"post埋篇文出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}